{
  "texts": [
    "We will also invite experts from different medical disciplines to test the reliability and usability of CHEER checklist.",
    "Additionally, we will create explanatory documents and examples to assist users of CHEER in better understanding and implementing the checklist.",
    "Furthermore, we plan to invite the consensus expert group members to translate CHEER into their local languages and promote the dissemination of the checklist.",
    "Additionally, we will actively reach out to journals, inviting them to feature CHEER on authors' instructions.",
    "Finally, we aim to establish a CHEER website to regularly update users on the latest developments and research findings related to CHEER reporting guidelines."
  ]
}